mil.nga.giat.geowave.vector.plugin

Class GeoWaveFeatureCollection

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.geotools.data.store.DataFeatureCollection
      • mil.nga.giat.geowave.vector.plugin.GeoWaveFeatureCollection
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.geotools.data.simple.SimpleFeatureCollection, org.geotools.feature.FeatureCollection<org.opengis.feature.simple.SimpleFeatureType,org.opengis.feature.simple.SimpleFeature>

    public class GeoWaveFeatureCollection
extends org.geotools.data.store.DataFeatureCollection
    This class is a helper for the GeoWave GeoTools data store. It represents a collection of feature data by encapsulating a GeoWave reader and a query object in order to open the appropriate cursor to iterate over data. It uses Keys within the Query hints to determine whether to perform special purpose queries such as decimation or distributed rendering.
